column2: SELECT TOP #      s.ra, s.dec,      s.z,      pz.z as phz ,pz.zErr as phzErr,           e.lgm_tot_p5#, e.lgm_tot_p8#, e.lgm_tot_p1#,   e.sfr_tot_p5#, e.sfr_tot_p8#, e.sfr_tot_p1#,   e.bptclass,      z.elliptical from zooSpec as z         JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS p ON p.specobjid = z.specobjid   JOIN Photoz AS pz ON pz.objID = p.objID   JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = z.specobjid   LEFT JOIN galSpecExtra AS e ON e.specobjid = z.specobjid   LEFT JOIN galSpecLine AS g ON g.specobjid=z.specobjid           WHERE      s.zwarning>#   AND p.petroMagErr_u > #   AND p.petroMagErr_g > #   AND p.petroMagErr_r > #   AND p.petroMagErr_i > #   AND p.petroMagErr_z > #      AND pz.zErr         > #   AND pz.photoErrorClass>#   AND z.elliptical=#
